<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">加项求积法，是指在两个乘数中有一个乘数是11，计算时，可先写上这个数首尾两数字，中间添写上相邻两数字依次相加的和（逢10要进1），此数就是要求的积。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">52×11=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 52×11</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=572</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>